### Feature Shift: Click-to-Add Node Generation
**1. The Change:** 
Implementing instant click-to-add functionality for the Node Palette.

**2. Explanation:** 
Originally, users could only add nodes to the canvas by dragging and dropping them from the sidebar. While intuitive, power users found this slow when rapidly assembling complex logic chains. By porting over the `handleAddNode` action and `onClick` bindings from the newer workspace, users can now quickly click any node in the list to spawn it instantly in the center of their current viewport viewport. This greatly accelerates workflow for experienced developers using the tool.

